      "line": null,
      "message": "Actually I don't know, how it is used,I just used the original code (https://github.com/codecentric/helm-charts/tree/master/charts/keycloakx)\nand modified the files, which were needed to run it in our environment.\nGenerally it would be better to not copy the code at all, but just include it and make modifications as an override.\nI heard, that some DT projects have done that and will check it for the next release...",
